Analyze String Typos

Source: R/table_different.R
table_different.Rd

Creates a table with rows that have different values than the rest of the other rows.

Usage

table_different(data, col_name, frequency = 5)

Arguments

data

dataframe The dataframe of information

col_name

character The name of column

frequency

numeric The maximum number of times a string can appear before it no longer appears on the table

Value

Returns a table with a list of row numbers and strings that showed up a fewer number of times than frequency

Examples

table_different(mouse_data_birth, "Treatment", 5)
